{"tid":413954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國旗國歌不敬的違法者並無罰則  憲法保障請願權  跪國歌不受罰","createTime":"2017-09-25T23:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T03:50:21.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e930558fe9c34e29eab9929884adb461b0477090","tid":413954,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"美保障請願權 跪國歌不受罰<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n特朗普強調風波與種族歧視無關。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n《美國國旗法》規定奏國歌時民眾須肅立、右手按心和面向國旗，但美國憲法第一修正案保障國民請願權和言論自由，對被指對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國旗國歌不敬的違法者並無罰則</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n但未來香港就可能不然，中國全國人大常委會早前通過《國歌法》，將在公共場合故意改歌詞、奏唱時不肅立不莊重列侮辱國歌行為，違者可被追究刑責，料下月實施後，將會納入《基本法》附件三在港實行，暫未知具體罰則。<br />\n《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"4a9d67c54fe3a7c420f546162832a697dc7b7b63","tid":413954,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bf7b3a4a485a61571f41d631fd1271490970c5","tid":413954,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:46:02.000Z","msg":"英 美 台可以用國旗圖案做衫"},{"pid":"0654fa67993d700473b8eacb3352c3a3783836a2","tid":413954,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:00:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Land of the free</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca57482e80b4b04a81ca9aa093d248d838c7bcff","tid":413954,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YTkUswT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYTkUswT.jpg&h=d2905269&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32505e8cc0499a21eb249a46ac3d14ec009